text: Alphonse Anger (20 October 1915 - 22 October 1999) was a French gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:1999 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Haut-Rhin
